<eesti> N&otilde;ukogu deklaratsioon </eesti>
<inglise> The Council will assess between now and the end of December 1999 Member States' compliance with their obligations under this joint action, with particular reference to implementation of Article 2 thereof. </inglise>
<eesti> N&otilde;ukogu hindab k&auml;esolevast hetkest kuni 1999. aasta detsembri l&otilde;puni liikmesriikide k&auml;esoleva &uuml;hismeetme kohaste kohustuste t&auml;itmist, v&otilde;ttes eelk&otilde;ige arvesse artikli 2 rakendamist. </eesti>
<inglise> It may then decide to continue this assessment on a regular basis. </inglise>
<eesti> Seej&auml;rel v&otilde;ib ta otsustada hindamist korrap&auml;raselt j&auml;tkata. </eesti>
<inglise> To that end, the Council will receive a report, based on the information provided by Member States, in accordance with the assessment mechanism adopted by the Council on 5 December 1997, which will: </inglise>
<eesti> Sel eesm&auml;rgil saab n&otilde;ukogu koosk&otilde;las 5. detsembril 1997 n&otilde;ukogu poolt vastu v&otilde;etud hindamismehhanismiga liikmesriikide poolt esitatud teabel p&otilde;hineva aruande, milles: </eesti>
<inglise> - describe progress in implementing this joint action, </inglise>
