<inglise> - consider any measure needed to achieve more effective judicial cooperation on the offences covered by this joint action, by examining inter alia time limits for judicial cooperation and whether the double criminality condition contained in national legislation hampers judicial cooperation between Member States, </inglise>
<eesti> - kirjeldatakse meetmeid, mis on vajalikud t&otilde;husama &otilde;igusalase koost&ouml;&ouml; saavutamiseks k&auml;esoleva &uuml;hismeetmega h&otilde;lmatud &otilde;igusrikkumiste osas, uurides muu hulgas &otilde;igusalase koost&ouml;&ouml; t&auml;htaegu ning seda, kas riikide seadustes sisalduv kahekordse karistatavuse tingimus takistab liikmesriikide vahelist &otilde;igusalast koost&ouml;&ouml;d, </eesti>
